      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you, she is a total showstopper! This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up. I\u2019ve pampered this car from day one, keeping it garage-stored and meticulously detailed. Not a scratch or a dent to be found! If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
