    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated precision. Featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, this example is mechanically impeccable. The PASM-equipped chassis remains taut, offering sublime lateral grip and telepathic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Every component, from the Brembo four-piston monobloc calipers to the flawlessly maintained valvetrain, reflects a standard of care synonymous with a showroom-fresh vehicle. With a pristine undercarriage and documented service history, this is an investment-grade driver\u2019s car optimized for peak performance.",
