    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the original trim remains rich and unfaded. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather is supple and shows no bolster wear, while the carpets are pristine. All electronics, from the climate control to the infotainment, function with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a meticulously documented service history and an engine bay kept in concours condition. This is a rare opportunity for a collector to own the finest example currently available.",
